        "type": "notes",
        "name": "Info",
        "position": { "col": 1, "row": 4 },
        "params": {
          "text": "PARTICLE CLOUD DEMO\n\nParticles create animated grain textures.\nX position = stereo pan\nY position = pitch variation\n\n- Turb: Chaos of particle movement\n- Gravity: Pull up/down (-1 to +1)\n- Mode: OSC uses internal oscillator\n         SMPL for sample loading\n         IN for external audio\n\nPlay keyboard to trigger burst.\nWatch particles dance in the canvas!"
